name: Let Me Stay in the Dark
description:
When people just learn about the good things, they never know when they do bad things. A lot of these things happens even on a person that we believe as a priest.
The brighter you seek the light, the darker shadow will be there.
That's how the dualism works, naturally.

Just let me stay in the dark.
Darker place i stay, my consciousness will shine brighter.
I could see tiniest small dots of light.

If you tired with the bright light,
Come join with me in the dark.
